    <item>
      <title>人类大脑已经神秘地保存了数千年</title>
      <link>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2423106-human-brains-have-been-mysteriously-preserved-for-thousands-of-years/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在沉船和被水淹没的坟墓等意想不到的地方发现了 12,000 年前或更久远的完整人类大脑，但尚不清楚是什么保存了它们]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.newscientist.com/article/2423106-human-brains-have-been-mysteriously-preserved-for-thousands-of-years/?utm_campaign=RSS%7CNSNS&amp;utm_source=NSNS&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_content=news</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 00:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
